      Apify
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ─── HOW IT WORKS ─── -->
<section class="section" id="how-it-works">
  <div class="section-label">Process</div>
  <h2 class="section-title">THREE STEPS TO YOUR NEXT ROLE</h2>
  <p class="section-sub">No manual job board browsing. No guessing. Just upload, search, and get ranked matches in under a minute.</p>

  <div class="steps-grid">
    <div class="step-card">
      <div class="step-number">01</div>
      <span class="step-icon">📄</span>
      <div class="step-title">UPLOAD YOUR RÉSUMÉ</div>
      <p class="step-desc">Paste your résumé text or upload a file. Tell us the role you want, your location, and preferred job sources.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="step-card">
      <div class="step-number">02</div>
      <span class="step-icon">⚡</span>
      <div class="step-title">WE SCRAPE LIVE JOBS</div>
      <p class="step-desc">Apify scrapers hit Indeed, LinkedIn, and Google Jobs in real-time — pulling fresh listings, not cached data.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="step-card">
      <div class="step-number">03</div>
      <span class="step-icon">🎯</span>
      <div class="step-title">AI RANKS YOUR MATCHES</div>
      <p class="step-desc">Claude AI scores every listing against your profile, identifies skill gaps, and gives you a personalised action plan.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<hr class="section-divider" />

<!-- ─── FEATURES ─── -->
<section class="section" id="features">
  <div class="section-label">Features</div>
  <h2 class="section-title">BUILT FOR JOB SEEKERS & RECRUITERS</h2>
  <p class="section-sub">Whether you're hunting your next role or sourcing top talent, Jobify gives you the edge.</p>

  <div class="features-grid">
    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-icon-wrap">🔍</div>
      <div>
        <div class="feature-title">Real-Time Scraping</div>
        <p class="feature-desc">Live data from Indeed, LinkedIn, and Google Jobs — scraped fresh on every search, not pulled from a stale database.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-icon-wrap">🧠</div>
      <div>
        <div class="feature-title">Claude AI Analysis</div>
        <p class="feature-desc">Every listing is scored against your résumé with percentage match scores, salary benchmarks, and fit reasoning.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-icon-wrap">📊</div>
      <div>
        <div class="feature-title">Skill Gap Detection</div>
        <p class="feature-desc">Instantly see which skills are holding you back and get a personalised roadmap to close the gap and land the role.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-icon-wrap">📋</div>
      <div>
        <div class="feature-title">Full HTML Reports</div>
